description:
Aspose.BarCode for .NET is a robust and reliable barcode generation and recognition component, written in managed C#, it allows developers to quickly and easily add barcode generation and recognition functionality to their Microsoft .NET applications (WinForms, ASP.NET and .NET Compact Framework). 

Aspose.BarCode for .NET supports most established barcode standards and barcode specifications. It has the ability to export to multiple image formats including: BMP, EMF, GIF, JPEG, PNG, TIFF and WMF.
releaseNotes:
Aspose.BarCode for .NET 4.9.0
Aspose.BarCode for .NET 4.9 has been released. Below is the list of new features and bug fixes included in this version.

New Features
BARCODENET-22738	IATA2of5 barcode generation for silverlight
BARCODENET-26465	Support OPC barcode generation for Silverlight
BARCODENET-33254	Support Code32 (Pharmacode)
BARCODENET-33259	Support adaptive binarization
BARCODENET-33268	Support Databar OmniDirectional (Recognition)
BARCODENET-33269	Support Databar Limited (Recognition)
BARCODENET-33270	Support Databar Expanded (Recognition)
BARCODENET-33275	Support Databar OmniDirectional (Generation)
BARCODENET-33276	Support Databar Limited (Generation)

Enhancements
BARCODENET-3433		Recognition for RM4SCC
BARCODENET-4602		Add support to get the codetext in byte array format when decoding
BARCODENET-20304	Enhance toolkit: add new recognition hints
BARCODENET-33208	Barcodes recognition improvement with vector algorithm support
BARCODENET-33240	Checksum feature requires changes
BARCODENET-33244	Make Symbology and BarcodeReadType enums with same order of items
BARCODENET-33264	BarcodeBuilder.DisplayText
BARCODENET-33271	Add Databar symbologies to toolkit (Recognition)

Bugs Fixed
BARCODENET-13824	Failed to recognize a scanned image (code39 type)
BARCODENET-17401	Aztec recognition error for tif case
BARCODENET-20187	Recognize GS1 Databar barcodes
BARCODENET-33228	Code93 recognition problem
BARCODENET-33231	IATA2of5 recognition doesnt work
BARCODENET-33232	Supplement recognition doesnt work
BARCODENET-33248	Turkish characters are not properly encoded with Pdf417
BARCODENET-33252	Cannot recognize Code39 from a PDF
BARCODENET-33253	Code39/93 changes
BARCODENET-33262	Online Documentation.url leads to nothing
BARCODENET-33263	Unable to encode Chinese characters with Pdf417
BARCODENET-33277	Cannot recognize QR from Pdf
BARCODENET-33280	Code128 BarCode not recognized
summary: Aspose.BarCode for .NET is a robust and reliable barcode generation and recognition component
